invalid type: string "PostgreSQL Scaling and Failover Runbook\r\nWhen CPU utilization exceeds 85% for more than 10 consecutive minutes, trigger \r\nthe read-replica auto-scaler via the AWS CLI. Primary database failover is automated \r\nvia Patroni. In the event of a split-brain scenario, immediately isolate the network \r\nnamespace of the old primary node to prevent data corruption.", expected a